# Contributors approved to bypass the issue/PR auto-close gate.
#
# Managed automatically by the approve-contributor workflow when a maintainer
# replies `lgtmi` (issues) or `lgtm` (issues + PRs) on an issue. Do not edit by
# hand unless you know what you are doing.
#
# Format: one entry per line — `<github-username> <issue|pr>`.
#   issue = the user's future issues stay open.
#   pr    = the user's future issues and PRs stay open.
